### Submit a new order
GET {{SalesApiStub_HostAddress}}/api/sales/products
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"customerId": "CUST-1001",
	"customerEmail": "customer@example.com",
	"shippingAddress": "123 Main St, Seattle, WA 98101",
	"items": [
		{
			"productId": 1,
			"quantity": 2
		},
		{
			"productId": 9,
			"quantity": 1
		}
	]
}

###

### Get identity details for current token
GET {{SalesApiStub_HostAddress}}/api/sales/my-info
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

